> 288fb seems to use "int 0x80"  and so do all the other system calls that
> I inspected.
>
> $ ls -l /lib/libc.so.6
> lrwxrwxrwx  1 root root 13 2005-08-09 22:28 /lib/libc.so.6 -> libc-2.3.5.so
